ther was also involved in. Otherwise there would be no reason for him to engage in it. Also, the reason that A gives for boredom is still tied to the feud. There are plenty of other ways that Gus could have dealt with boredom but he specifically chose space fighting *because* of the feud that has been going on for generations."}}]}}}},{"JudgeFeedback":{"distribution":[0.99,0.010000000000000007],"feedback":{"speaker":"Bubbles Brandywine","timestamp":1677258216064,"content":[{"Text":{"text":"The fact that the father doesn't show up (or B didn't provide it when explicitly asked) makes me extremely skeptical of B. I resolve for A with high confidence on this basis."}}]},"endDebate":true}},{"OfflineJudgments":{"judgments":{"Elmo Eggplant":{"mode":"stepped","startTimeMillis":1684528991634,"judgments":[{"distribution":[0.5,0.5],"feedback":{"speaker":"Elmo Eggplant","timestamp":1684528992956,"content":[]},"endDebate":false},{"distribution":[0.5,0.5],"feedback":{"speaker":"Elmo Eggplant","timestamp":1684528995086,"content":[]},"endDebate":false},{"distribution":[0.99,0.01],"feedback":{"speaker":"Elmo Eggplant","timestamp":1684529369089,"content":[{"Text":{"text":"This round seems pretty easy based on the lack of evidence surrounding the existence of the father while the boredom stuff is directly evidenced. B doesn't really have a response to the boredom ev."}}]},"endDebate":true}]}}}}],"feedback":{"Bubbles Brandywine":{"Judge":{"answers":{"factual informativeness (comparative)":{"first":2,"second":2},"evidence in debate":{"first":2,"second":0},"judge adaptation":{"first":4,"second":1},"clarity":{"first":3,"second":3},"factual informativeness (total)":2,"judge reasoning":4,"judge strategies":"I asked for evidence that the father was impactful in the story. Debater A (honest) responded saying that the father wasn't even mentioned. Debater B (dishonest) didn't address this point.","reason for outcome":"Honest debater claimed that a crucial part of dishonest's answer was not fin